WEBVTT

00:00:29.753 --> 00:00:31.991
Those are just a few
of the horrific stories

00:00:32.015 --> 00:00:34.523
that I heard from women
over the last year,

00:00:34.547 --> 00:00:37.726
as I've been investigating
workplace sexual harassment.

00:00:38.236 --> 00:00:40.385
And what I found out

00:00:40.409 --> 00:00:43.225
is that it's an epidemic across the world.

00:00:44.307 --> 00:00:47.622
It's a horrifying reality
for millions of women,

00:00:47.646 --> 00:00:49.760
when all they want to do every day

00:00:49.784 --> 00:00:51.204
is go to work.

00:00:52.998 --> 00:00:55.247
Sexual harassment doesn't discriminate.

00:00:55.886 --> 00:00:57.268
You can wear a skirt,

00:00:57.799 --> 00:00:59.371
hospital scrubs,

00:00:59.395 --> 00:01:00.683
army fatigues.